joshua ( also known as the devil 's child ) is a 2007 american psychological thriller horror film about an affluent young manhattan family and how they are torn apart by the increasingly sadistic behavior of their disturbed son , joshua . the film was directed and co-written by george ratliff , and stars sam rockwell , vera farmiga and jacob &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it was released on july 6 , 2007 in the united states by fox searchlight pictures .